大雨先濕完身<br />\n又可以明正言順喺馬路露lin 爽！"},{"pid":"199287ac0a312c2465abf832b788f6826144b909","tid":310061,"uid":3362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"報左先<br />\nPass左可以唔揸<br />\n但冇報又成日心思思<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 考完驚死冇揸"},{"pid":"9fca6caca9bb39c6625bda0b8d10e8960f38c816","tid":310061,"uid":105632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學多樣嘢<br />\n考到先再諗養唔養車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7af784e017105171c40cfa6a1651798c56ac0b","tid":310061,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:09:08.000Z","msg":"求介紹邊度學<br />\n利申1，2牌11年了"},{"pid":"cfb5295c196f40fef531b7cd57e9f0e5169448cd","tid":310061,"uid":42042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T17:09:38.000Z","msg":"要瞞就唔好喇"},{"pid":"cd99efae00e0931b91e7e85e45f2d71674281b83","tid":310061,"uid":94218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報左先<br />\nPass左可以唔揸<br />\n但冇報又成日心思思<br />\n<br />\n利伸： 考完驚死冇揸</blockquote><br />\n唔考真係心思思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外請問各位巴打<br />\n如果想快啲考到係咪 觀駕強制+港島師傅？"},{"pid":"9d4a2b88244ae05f7786809aa4fa7e3072b7ec9c","tid":310061,"uid":94218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T17:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家有1 2正牌<br />\n自己其實想考，但屋企人話危險<br />\n諗緊好唔好瞞住佢哋去考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想考原因係希望有部車仔代下步<br />\n但仲返緊學養唔起46<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲可唔可以俾少少意見！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你同你屋企人講<br />\n死唔死既野整定既<br />\n行出街都可以比招牌壓死<br />\n<br />\n當時我係咁同我阿媽講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過其實有時我會諗，就算信得過自己，都信唔過其他道路使用者。<br />\n就好似一年前嘅凌晨，三號仔七人車撞死咗個綿羊仔司機，就會淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d3095e2cdf58a47d75c73b43df880c41d090bd","tid":310061,"uid":119405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T17:23:18.000Z","msg":"本身暪住女朋友考<br />\n報咗駕院俾曬錢上咗一堂老強<br />\n點知俾佢發現咗無得考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450f0608d6057b118793e1ebb9b15b41a633acec","tid":310061,"uid":33826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T17:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身暪住女朋友考<br />\n報咗駕院俾曬錢上咗一堂老強<br />\n點知俾佢發現咗無得考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得你咁樣而唔去學埋係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d236636c19ec5e8439a5972a0286fb8b766370a5","tid":310061,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身暪住女朋友考<br />\n報咗駕院俾曬錢上咗一堂老強<br />\n點知俾佢發現咗無得考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得你咁樣而唔去學埋係好<del>可惜</del><span style=\"color: red;\">on9</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1dc2918fd2e719c760662e13f551ed845e8578fd","tid":310061,"uid":6778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:59:56.000Z","msg":"當你坐左上架電單車度. 你會覺得個世界係你既. 種感覺沒野取代到<br />\n同識到好多朋友"},{"pid":"0287f89695e0c9cc852ef3583cbb8c4cd2864a4e","tid":310061,"uid":19722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:31:17.000Z","msg":"都係車一部<br />\n唔好以為好型而去考<br />\n自己諗清楚"},{"pid":"f966aaa4b5754eac19fb4ab1f1431f706f9a3277","tid":310061,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:53:16.000Z","msg":"其實真係幾危險<br />\n有時前面有大車<br />\n一粒石仔打埋嚟都好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考牌真係要諗清楚<br />\n考個牌接近一皮嘢"},{"pid":"fd62072f4ff9822